of technology in cambridge mass that does not set minoxidil 
apart 
although the drug may affect hair follicles there is no reason 
to believe that the drug would have similar effects on other types 
of cells weinberg said 
weinberg said the research would have been more convincing had 
it identified a specific gene or group of genes affected by the 
drug upjohn spokeswoman kaye bennett said the researchers hadnt 
identified a specific gene 
