jobs would be lost over the next 40 years if significant stands of 
oldgrowth timber were set aside to save the owls at the same 
time she said 26500 jobs would be lost due to mill modernization 
conservationists recognize that achieving a healthy economy 
for the northwests timberdependent area is part of the picture by 
