said 
being in rome has affected me as a writer americans have a 
poor sense of history and you cant walk around rome without being 
immersed in history 
its inspiring drinking at a cafe where goethe drank and 
standing in the cemetery where keats is buried theres no 
doubt ill be writing about rome in one way or the other for many 
years to come 
