company with a substantial connection to minnesota by selling the 
companys assets 
give the metropolitan airports commission power to approve an 
acquisition of a major tenant of minneapolisst paul international 
airport such as northwest 
impose a state excise tax on golden parachutes the large 
severance payments corporate executives receive if they are fired 
or leave their jobs after their company is bought 
