luring back striking pilots who would lose seniority if they took 
jobs at rival carriers 
under the plan which would cut eastern jobs from the prestrike 
31200 to around 17000 management reckons it would need about 
1700 pilots the airline says it is hiring and training new pilots 
at the rate of around 200 a month 
