mean the industry could experience reregulation he said if 
the barriertoentry problems are not resolved that will happen 
beauvais said concern over the situation is starting to register 
in washington but that it will take such things as even higher 
prices and theyre going to get a lot higher and several major 
failures to bring concerted reform efforts 
